1. Create a Pizza class
2. Set the default values for a pizza (large, pepperoni, hand-tossed crust.)
4. Make the mutator functions (sets the size, type, instructions, and crust type)
5. Make the accessors (gets the size, type, instructions, and crust type.)
6. Make the toString method (format: Ordering: [a/an] (size) (type) pizza)
7. In the main function, use the mutators to change the pizza. Every change, print out pizza.toString().